Prerequisites

You should have development version of Qt5.

Compiling & Installing Idiomind

1. If you want to change default installation prefix (/usr/local/bin), use PREFIX environment variable.
   Note that installation directory should be in PATH environment variable
2. run `qmake` - this will create Makefile
3. run `make` - this will compile Idiomind sources
4. run `make install` - this will install Idiomind into chosen directory and create a shortcut in menu
5. to start Idiomind use the shortcut in menu, or `idiomind` command
